<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, June 16 (Xinhua) -- A Kuwaiti company, the M.A
Kharafi Group, plans to put a multi billion Tanzanian Shillings
investment on off-shore banking and tourist resort project at
Nungwi Peninsular in Zanzibar.
</P>
<P>
The Zanzibar Investment Company Limited (ZICO) Project
Director, Herbert Law, told reporters in Dar es Salaam today that
the group's investment during the first three years was estimated
