<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Tribute to Deng Xiaoping's Contribution to Hong Kong' Return -- Xinhua Commentary (6) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Showing his deep concern for the reunification of the
motherland, Deng said: "China's reunification is the aspiration of
all the Chinese people"; "we are determined to achieve the
reunification that has not yet been done"; "the compatriots in the
mainland, Taiwan, Hong Kong, and Macao, as well as the overseas
Chinese are all offspring of the Chinese nation. We should strive
together for the reunification of the motherland and the
rejuvenation of the nation."
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping's outstanding contribution to the reunification
of the motherland will go down in history.
</P>
<P>
The Communist Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at the
core will adhere to Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism
with Chinese characteristics. While attaching great importance to
economic development to strengthen the country, the Central
Committee will follow the "one country, two systems" principle,
exercise strong leadership in the return of Hong Kong despite all
kinds of interference, and make a tremendous contribution to
realizing the goal of transition, prosperity and stability in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
We believe that, after this important step in the reunification
of the motherland, we will certainly be able to follow the
orientation set by Deng Xiaoping to solve the Taiwan question
appropriately, reunify the motherland completely, and create a new
turning point for the Chinese nation to live up to the
expectations of the great patriot, Comrade Deng Xiaoping, and the
millions of martyrs who advanced wave upon wave for a unified
motherland and a powerful and prosperous nation from 1840 on.
</P>
</TEXT>
