George Saitoti said today.
</P>
<P>
He made the remarks when meeting with the delegation of
Chinese People's Association for Friendship with Foreign
Countries led by Qian Zhengying, Vice-Chairman of the Chinese
People's Political Consultative Conference.
</P>
