He spoke highly of China's long-term contribution to the
eastern African country in various fields including construction,
medicine, agriculture and road-mending.
</P>
<P>
Qian said the Chinese government attaches great importance to
its ties with Kenya and is satisfied with the smooth and fruitful
bilateral relations over the past years through the
exchange of visits from top leaders.
</P>
<P>
Her visit aims to seek for more ways of cooperation between
the two peoples, Qian said.
</P>
<P>
Qian's delegation arrived here this morning and will leave on
Saturday. 
</P>
