<HEADLINE> Zambian Non-traditional Exports in High Demands </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Seventeen companies from 12
countries are seeking to import Zambian non-traditional products,
particularly agricultural ones, information from the Export Board
of Zambia (EBZ) revealed.
</P>
<P>
The companies are from the United States, India, Pakistan,
Chile, the Ukraine, the United Arab Emirates (UAE), the
Netherlands, Hungary, Moldovia, the Czech Republic, Russia and
