Ukraine company wants 50,000 tons of raw sugar to process,
whereas an Indian company setting demands for cattle gall stones
in large quantity.
</P>
<P>
Zambia has, in recent years, made efforts to boost
non-traditional exports in addition to its conventional copper.
Hence the set-up of the EBZ some years ago. 
