<HEADLINE> Shanghai Students Greet Return of Hong Kong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Some 150,000 university students
in Shanghai have been participating in a variety of activities to
greet the return of Hong Kong to the motherland.
</P>
<P>
In Shanghai's Jiaotong University, teachers compiled a special
textbook on Hong Kong and offered the course for the school's
10,000 students.
